    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Mamaearth Capital India - Freshers Welcome",
    "description": "Join the Mamaearth Capital India family as a Marketplace Manager in Delhi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Mamaearth Capital India:\nMamaearth Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mamaearth Capital India!",
